                <p class="testquote">"Ours is a 60 bed hospital with more than 15 resident and visiting Doctors. SM Tejas is the only product in the market which can integrate all aspects of running a hospital. The Doctor's pages are really helpful. The Management gets all reports on daily basis. We can now control and manage every aspect. Thanks to Samarth Meditech and wish them good luck."</p>
                <p class='testname'>Dr | Venkatesh AL</p>
