                <p class='testname'>Mr. Satish Kulkarni</p>
                <p class="testwork">Manikya medicals Belagavi.</p>
            </div>                                
        </div>
        <div class="testbox hide">
            <div class="testquotes">
                <p class="testquote">"I did not trust SM Daksha till I started using it. I am now already used to it and cannot run the clinic without SM Daksha. The scribble pad is a great idea and makes it paperfree and easy. Great job Samarth Meditech for a great product."</p>
                <p class='testname'>Dr | Sheetal patil</p>
                <p class="testwork">Chirayu clinic.</p>
            </div>                                     
        </div>
        <div class="testbox hide">
            <div class="testquotes">
                <p class="testquote">"The Advanceed Accounting Features SM Shodha are really great! All the features are well thought. We have been looking for these features for long and finally found them in SM Shodha. The support and training from Samarth Meditech has been great and I would recommend SM Shodha to all."</p>
